---
name    : detroit-email
version : 0.1.0
title   : Detroit Email
summary : Email plugin for Detroit

authors:
  - T.Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

description:
  Email plugin for Detroit build system.
  This plugin is designed to send out a well
  formated release announcement during the
  promote phase. Though, it can be configured
  to send out any message desired.

requirements:
  - detroit

resources:
  home: http://detroit.github.com/
  code: http://github.com/detroit/detroit-email
  mail: http://groups.google.com/group/rubyworks-mailinglist

